        }
      ],
      "text": "Pong was a minor government official who had recently moved into the affluent Upper Ring of Ba Sing Se after Team Avatar arrived at the capital. He occupied the house across from Team Avatar's Upper Ring house."
    },
    {
      "body": "After ${link_0} had left Team Avatar at their new home, ${link_1} noticed Pong spying on them from his home across the street. When Sokka questioned him regarding the ${link_2}, Pong hesitated at answering. When he was asked to explain his awkward, dismissive behavior, he stated he did not want to get in any trouble, furthering that he had waited three years to acquire his house. Pong warned ${link_3} and his friends to not mention the War within the walls, to look out for the ${link_4}, and to stay away from them. This showed that Pong was well aware of the Dai Li's control over the populace of Ba Sing Se.",
      "links": [
        {
          "body": "Joo Dee",
